oads forever\r\n2. lack of tests - Glance is allegedly unit testable, but because this access `LocalContext`, it would need to provided by something like Robolectric, which I did not think was worth importing for that alone. there's otherwise very little logic here, but happy to eventually add tests for the Repository etc if preferred\r\n3. I can't get the \"Refreshing\" text to actually display for some reason - though it does if I make that the only content. I'll probably keep messing with this at some point\r\n4. widget isn't resizable\r\n\r\nLMK your thoughts on whether any of these are worth baking longer - happy to keep trucking on this but it's obviously been slow going. Assume we will just squash these commits as well?\r\n\r\n[Screen_recording_20260106_222913.webm](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0802ecd2-49d4-4ad4-9039-08685bbe85f8)\r\n\r\nFixes #384\r\n","created_at":"2026-01-07T06:29:54Z","updated_at":"2026-03-02T16:57:10Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"2487a07cf65cde43435a6cb563c952464ce28048","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/spacecowboy/Feeder/pulls/1018/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/spacecowboy/Feeder/pulls/1018/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/spacecowboy/Feeder/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/spacecowboy/Feeder/issues/1018/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/spacecowboy/Feeder/statuses/975a876e1e0f33728d8fd670dff7ed7e5926c990","head":{"label":"MatthewTighe:add-widget","ref":"add-widget","sha":"975a876e1e0f33728d8fd670dff7ed7e5926c990","user":{"login":"MatthewTighe","id":10427470,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNDI3NDcw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10427470?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/MatthewTighe","html_url":"https://github.com/MatthewTighe","